SIMPLE: subkingdom
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subkingdom
<hw>Sub*king"dom</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the
several primary divisions of either the animal, or vegetable kingdom,
as, in Zoology, the Vertebrata, Tunicata, Mollusca, Articulata,
Molluscoidea, Echinodermata, Coelentera, and the Protozoa; in botany,
the Phanerogamia, and the Cryptogamia.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sublapsarian</ent>⟦br⟧
